'''卡蒂雅·洛涵'''（{{lang-de|Katja Loher}}，{{bd|1979年}}）是一位出生于[[苏黎世|苏黎世]]的瑞士视觉艺术家，尤其以视觉雕塑和装置作品而闻名。她擅長將有机物、宇宙星体和移动舞蹈的元素整合於作品中，在她的作品中可以看到时间的流动以及空间的变幻。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Structures Awards|url=https://www.bizjournals.com/southflorida/news/2017/11/10/structures-awards-2017-learn-more.html|access-date=2020-09-17|website=www.bizjournals.com|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101100021/https://www.bizjournals.com/southflorida/news/2017/11/10/structures-awards-2017-learn-more.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=The House Collective's art programme with Swiss artist Katja Loher concludes at The Temple House|url=https://www.buro247.sg/culture/art-and-design/the-house-collective-debut-art-programme-with-swiss-artist-katja-loher-concludes-at-the-temple-house-in-chengdu-china.html|access-date=2020-09-17|website=BURO.|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922131749/https://www.buro247.sg/culture/art-and-design/the-house-collective-debut-art-programme-with-swiss-artist-katja-loher-concludes-at-the-temple-house-in-chengdu-china.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的艺术作品已在意大利、俄罗斯、中国、美国等多个国家的著名美术馆展出，<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=MAXXI Newsletter|url=http://www.maxxi.art/newsletter/30062010/newsletter_eng.html|access-date=2020-09-17|website=www.maxxi.art|archive-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403161117/https://www.maxxi.art/newsletter/30062010/newsletter_eng.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=: Katja Loher's Video World :|url=http://www.784.kunafin.com/floating_rendezvous.htm|access-date=2020-09-16|website=www.784.kunafin.com|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009195451/http://www.784.kunafin.com/floating_rendezvous.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{cite web|title=The 3rd China International Installation Art Academic Forum and China International Installation Art Exhibition|url=http://www.todayartmuseum.com/cnexhd